verbose_text: The annual rate of change, R, of the response ratio ln (RR), show that overall GI decreased SOC, with an annual rate of -0.009 (-0.9%; StDev = 0.037), but increased pH at a rate of 0.003 (+0.3%; StDev = 0.006), TN at a rate of 0.0005 (+0.05%; StDev = 0.0047) and BD at a rate of 0.009 (+0.09%; StDev = 0.021).
